Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林  松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫罗兰\N莲藕…唉呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令尊的知交\N在这么偏僻的森林中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的好  我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从空中传来声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想差不多\N该是你来的时候了  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就知道我会来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朴仙翁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来找我是为了刀的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第51话 犬夜叉的心被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我追琥珀的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有毒蜂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连毒蜂也吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你去追珊瑚还有戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜牺牲自己战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了我和琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你之后我也会自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把你从奈落手里夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我而害你\N吸入了那些毒虫的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊…瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一副那么难过的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的事情…还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  不要  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  我打水来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的遗物  铁碎牙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树木妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷  这东西到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树龄两千年的朴树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且杀生丸的父亲所遗留的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙与天生牙的刀鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是用我的枝干削出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀鞘…原来那把刀的刀鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用这家伙的枝干做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀鞘不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这家伙也就可想而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朴仙翁  你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与铁碎牙的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…你同父异母的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的血已经变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次是铁碎牙\N被鬼咬碎的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次是和我缠斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开铁碎牙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从半妖之血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成和我与父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪之血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的妖怪之血吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉是\N妖怪与人类所生的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法成为真正的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和你不同  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯碎的妖怪的你做得到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对犬夜叉而言是却做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉做不到的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是  保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  好比说杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从来没有在战斗中\N被逼得走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而心灰意冷到失去自我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把我逼到走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许真是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在走投无路  生命垂危的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪之血就会支配身体而妖化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉从你父亲身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承的大妖怪之血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对半妖的身体而言太强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来  会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心会被妖怪之血吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己是谁都分不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会敌我不分的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在不断反覆妖化中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一日犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会完全丧失理智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后化身为只会战斗的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续战斗至身体毁灭为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲应该不希望\N犬夜叉变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会将当作\N护身之刀的铁碎牙交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙是护身之刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它放开的时候  犬夜叉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得犬夜叉成熟多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在夸奖你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  你救了琥珀一命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想\N让奈落称心如意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能让琥珀活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一定会气个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在说反话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也有点不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犬夜叉一直没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口还很痛吧?让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  我自己治疗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好彻底治疗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是更严重怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我是想道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道谢  是指什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们  戈薇  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们陪伴着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪伴着她?那是应该的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音从那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爷爷  我爷爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里  老头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙没有妖怪的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里  在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚不小心踩空了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什~么~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为妖怪出现\N让人担心个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扭到脚正不知所措呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙各位这样照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里  举手之劳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就别放在心上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么您保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妖怪狗哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的宝物送给你当谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给了你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇蜕下的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蛇的蜕皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢  犬夜叉给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就没有时间去帮别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是举手之劳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次做了好事之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定会变的很不爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且人数还不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒起烟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是刚才老头\N与小鬼的村子的方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们被什么袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  治疗一下小鬼的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你留在这里保护戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这村子我很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在食物吃完前就待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人通通集中在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的就杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是强盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些小喽罗等等再收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫头目出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  强盗群中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有只妖怪混在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子…你的刀挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然率领着强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目是妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  那把刀交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?你还没睡醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我会输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不交出那把刀  我就用抢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  抢得到就来抢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉应该还无法随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用很重的铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要扒掉你那伪装的皮  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊!头目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目的大钺被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是锋利的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的话就纳命来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有面盾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经中了我的毒粉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是把好刀  我愈来愈中意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我是妖怪就怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么厉害的妖怪当头目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是无敌的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会像以前一样跟随您的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  活该
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是毒茧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不留神碰到的话会融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的家伙\N马上就会尸骨无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是毒茧  一直碰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是谁都会溶化的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那些家伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有溶化?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从内部张开了结界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你还能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种烂茧我马上撕破它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体无法动弹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才让你淋到的毒粉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经从伤口进入体内了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一步步去见阎王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目请
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被铁碎牙的结界拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么刀会拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的铁碎牙会选择主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说像你这种杂碎妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不配持有它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是这些\N杂碎般的人类强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被刀选上的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说杂碎太狠了吧  头目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个半妖对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太滑稽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个区区的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢向我妖怪蛾天丸找碴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了  一定是在村子出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但没有好  反而愈来愈大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  血止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毒粉的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是张开结界就很勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法活动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这结界能撑到什么时候呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  头目  这把刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你处置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对不能用的刀没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢头目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把刀无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非交给那个人不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把刀真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界破掉  被毒茧融化\N是迟早的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里等着看好戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把女孩带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:30.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:42.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:49.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:58.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:05.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:12.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:19.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:27.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:35.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被毒蛾妖怪蛾天丸\N困在毒茧中的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到凶猛的妖怪之血支配
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不留情的杀光强盗们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能解除犬夜叉的妖化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想个让他恢复原状的办法
